{"tid":1183002,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[傳聞] Marvel 傳聞傾緊Keanu Reeves拍永恆族","createTime":"2019-06-02T15:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T17:38:23.000Z","uid":171975,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"08adf9471ba0263be08860a534aa07ba8a158f26","tid":1183002,"uid":171975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會d fans屌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都成日俾人話d戲屎<br />\n咁 DC Constantine 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Keanu Reeves is Being Sought For a Role in &lsquo;The Eternals&rsquo; </strong><br />\n<br />\nIf you&rsquo;ve followed MCU Cosmic over the last year, you&rsquo;ll know this site has been on top of The Eternals since the very beginning when the news first broke of Marvel&rsquo;s newest franchise. Now I have a small bit of news about that movie, from the same reliable source who first told me of The Eternals (and other things that have come true).<br />\n<br />\nKeanu Reeves is being sought for a role in The Eternals, and negotiations are apparently underway already. He&rsquo;s not signed yet and this is all still early, and I don&rsquo;t know what role he&rsquo;s being considered for.<br />\n<br />\nI usually don&rsquo;t bother with casting scoops, but given this source I&rsquo;m confident in putting this out there. Again, it&rsquo;s still early and sounds like negotiations are pretty recent. Still, I know Marvel fans have dreamed of seeing Keanu show up in the MCU (there&rsquo;s fan art out there of him as Wolverine), and I personally thought he&rsquo;d make a great Silver Surfer; but it seems like The Eternals is where he may end up.<br />\n<br />\nIf things work out, and he does end up in the movie, then The Eternals is shaping up to have a pretty strong cast that already includes Angelina Jolie and Richard Madden.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mcucosmic.com/2019/06/01/keanu-reeves-is-being-sought-for-a-role-in-the-eternals-exclusive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcucosmic.com%2F2019%2F06%2F01%2Fkeanu-reeves-is-being-sought-for-a-role-in-the-eternals-exclusive%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=8148f1be\" target=\"_blank\">https://mcucosmic.com/2019/06/01/keanu-reeves-is-being-sought-for-a-role-in-the-eternals-exclusive/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://comicbook.com/marvel/2019/06/02/marvel-studios-keanu-reeves-star-the-eternals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcomicbook.com%2Fmarvel%2F2019%2F06%2F02%2Fmarvel-studios-keanu-reeves-star-the-eternals%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=db9371ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://comicbook.com/marvel/2019/06/02/marvel-studios-keanu-reeves-star-the-eternals/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbr.com/john-wick-keanu-reeves-eternals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.com%2Fjohn-wick-keanu-reeves-eternals%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a69f07fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbr.com/john-wick-keanu-reeves-eternals/</a>"},{"pid":"7c25cf6138316cc1f2bc1441f96f017c6add83fe","tid":1183002,"uid":75050,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"John Wick is a man of focus"},{"pid":"1b989599cb159b24382829316b76d22953146a1f","tid":1183002,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"Keanu Reeves is a character played by the Eternal"},{"pid":"55c82d0764b9ad6007a943e5c0c5a97fef6efdfd","tid":1183002,"uid":171975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"《The Eternals》是由Marvel漫畫家Jack Kirby於1976年創作，是數百萬年前的古老人類，由天神族透過實驗而創造。擁有強大的操控心靈和宇宙的能力，而他們最大的敵人便是「The Deviants」。《復仇者聯盟3》中，Thanos便是「The Eternals」與「The Deviants」混合而生的生物。<br />\n<br />\n《TheEternals》將會由亞裔女導演Chloe Zhao執導，而Chloe Zhao也在之前有執導過不同的電影，最出名的就是大家都耳熟能詳的《重生騎士The Rider》。而《The Eternals》也將會成為MCU中非常重要的電影之一，或會成為《Avengers》電影中的救世主！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MvDUT6e2y5hjavR8B8bH1A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/a5e32afc016cbd57e0fb31db135cff73\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMvDUT6e2y5hjavR8B8bH1A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fa5e32afc016cbd57e0fb31db135cff73&h=ebb16a74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15af91d06b952b22f89e8a51824d3fcb6f52c309","tid":1183002,"uid":25327,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T22:04:26.000Z","msg":"拍返魔間行者先唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefed295b140ba11620448c7c1363a1c14980a34","tid":1183002,"uid":84081,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7c25cf6138316cc1f2bc1441f96f017c6add83fe","tid":1183002,"uid":75050,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"John Wick is a man of focus"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T22:56:21.000Z","msg":"Commitment <br />\nAnd sheer fucking will."},{"pid":"373a48b3c7dc3de59e3eb303ab1e0513994ebd84","tid":1183002,"uid":60028,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"奇洛上年曾經表示過想演Wolverine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8172e204bd62dac0a8f937fb09c0282bea38a4","tid":1183002,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:34:33.000Z","msg":"《TheEternals》將會由<span style=\"color: red;\">亞裔</span><span style=\"color: green;\">女導演</span>Chloe Zhao執導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /